# Discord IP-CIDR
IP-CIDR,104.29.138.0/24,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,104.29.141.0/24,no-resolve

# Discord Voice Server IP 段（66.22.196.0 ~ 66.22.249.255）
# 原始 27 个 /23 合并为 6 个 CIDR
IP-CIDR,66.22.196.0/22,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.22.200.0/21,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.22.208.0/20,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.22.224.0/20,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.22.240.0/21,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,66.22.248.0/23,no-resolve

# ===== Process =====
# Node.js 进程（OpenClaw gateway + 脚本）
# Discord Voice UDP 发到动态 IP（Fastly/Google/Facebook 等多 ASN），
# 域名规则无法匹配裸 IP，用 PROCESS-NAME 兜底
PROCESS-NAME,node
